snippet.textDisplay: Beautiful piece and rightly matched… এই Season -এ personally, I was missing the cohesion. Coke studio is about uniqueness, about celebrating the culture and most iconic part is - its about being ‘carefully careless’ while joining two songs. Except Murir Tin, Deora and of course this song - I was finding season 2 songs either too flat or mixed in a weird way. Thank you for creating such a wonderful piece… welcome back Coke Studio Bangla, Season 2!
